        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Lobbyist Loophole Closure Act</b></p> <p>This bill broadens the scope of lobbying activities that trigger lobbyist registration and disclosure requirements. </p> <p>Specifically, it expands lobbying activities to include legislative, political, and strategic counseling services.</p>]]>
        </text>
